REFERRED TO HOUSING, CONSTRUCTION AND COMMUNITY DEVELOPMENT

Title: Relates to the selection of tenants in state aided housing projects in the county of Westchester
Summary: Permits the county of Westchester to grant a fifty percent preference in the selection of tenants in state aided housing projects to current residents of the county.
LawCode: Add ยง156-d, Pub Hous L
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the public housing law, in relation to the selection of tenants in state aided housing projects in the county of Westchester
